Noah's Ark - Far From the Truth
The Good ... the special effects and the parts of the movie that stuck to the biblical account of the story were interesting ... however - the bad - there was soooooo much that was added THAT WAS NOT IN THE ORIGINAL BIBLICAL ACCOUNT that I found the movie was a big disappointment and it actually made it boring - there was no need to add all the extra story lines - it was silly and actually detracted from the main topic.  I would not recommend this movie to anyone ...

