Overview



Though long (because it began life as a television miniseries), Noah's Ark on DVD comes with very little: an English audio track (Dolby Digital 2.0 Surround), a standard full-screen picture with an aspect ratio of 1.33:1, dual layering, closed-captions, and a theatrical trailer. Some of these rather standard features are listed as special ones on the plastic DVD case, which also contains a chapter index, a few production notes, and plenty of advertising. Sound and picture quality are uninspiringly adequate.


